entries.entry: There's so many poorly chosen words in that sentence. I hear the jury's still out on science. Really? Did nothing cancel? That's why you always leave a note! That's why you always leave a note! Marry me.

Oh, I don't have time for this. I have to go and buy a single piece of fruit with a coupon and then return it, making people wait behind me while I complain. But existing is basically all I do! This opera's as lousy as it is brilliant! Your lyrics lack subtlety. You can't just have your characters announce how they feel. That makes me feel angry!
